= Wavemon

无线网络监视工具

{{wavemon/uploads/wavemon.png|wovemon.png}}


== 其它命令

<<code bash>>
$ iwconfig wlan0 | grep -i --color signal
Link Quality=41/70  Signal level=-69 dBm

$ watch -n 1 cat /proc/net/wireless
<</code>>

